('6755', '4', 'Heat a skillet on medium heat and spray with olive oil. Cook tilapia for about 3-4 minutes per side.Once fish is cooked, flake it with a fork and mix with chopped shallots, chopped avocado, remaining lime zest, cilantro and/or mint. I loved the combination or cilantro and mint, but I would suggest trying it before making an entire bowl of it.'),
