('6756', '6', 'Transfer the fish to the platter in the oven to keep warm while you cook the remaining two fillets.'),
('6756', '7', 'Transfer the fillets to the platter and spoon half of the salsa on top.'),
('6756', '8', 'Serve with the remaining salsa on the side.*Note: Puree a little little bit of the salsa with or with out the fish for puree eating babies. You can also spoon pureed salsa over little flakes of fishand a steamed grain, if you have itfor children eating textured foods.'),
