('6761', '1', 'Preheat oven to 450F. In a small bowl, mix garlic powder, chili powder, salt, black pepper and cayenne. Sprinkle evenly over both sides of tilapia.Coat a baking sheet with 1 tablespoon of the oil. Arrange tilapia in a single layer on the baking sheet. drizzle with the remaining tablespoon of oil.'),
