('6771', '6', 'Add the tilapia and reduce heat to medium. Cook for one to two minutes, and then flip. Continue cooking until cooked through (only a few minutes depending on thickness).'),
('6771', '7', 'Remove from heat.To plate, spoon some soft polenta onto a plate. Top with a piece of fish and finish with fresh squeezed lemon juice. Enjoy!Source for Ingredientsfarm-raised tilapia, Cajun seasoning, organic thyme and polenta from Whole Foods'),
