('6787', '7', 'Brush olive oil on the spice-rubbed fish and place onto the grill. Cook 3-4 minutes on each side until the fish is fork tender & gently flakes. Plate grilled fish and sprinkle each serving with lime juice.'),
('6787', '8', 'Add 1 1/2 tablespoons of salsa on top of each filet and serve with fresh spinach or steamed broccoli!Enjoy!'),
