('6804', '2', 'Heat 1 tablespoon olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat. Cook onion and red pepper in the oil until onion is tender and golden, and peppers are slightly soft, about 10 minutes.  Stir balsamic vinegar into the vegetables. season with salt and pepper.'),
('6804', '3', 'Rub tilapia filets with 2 teaspoons olive oil and a sprinkle of salt and pepper.'),
