('6810', '5', 'Serve the tilapia accompanied by the dipping sauce.'),
('6811', '1', 'Brush both sides of fish with dressing. place on greased rack of broiler pan.  Broil, 6 inches from heat, 8 min. or until fish flakes easily with fork.'),
