('6843', '3', 'Add mushrooms and onions. cook and stir 5 min.'),
('6843', '4', 'Add couscous. cook and stir 1 min. Stir in broccoli and broth.  Bring to boil. cover.  Simmer 8 min. or until liquid is absorbed.'),
('6843', '5', 'Meanwhile, place fish in shallow pan sprayed with cooking spray.'),
